&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain deep insights in the Fashion Nova Consumer by understanding their desires, needs, preferences, and shopping experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a comprehensive understanding of the competitive landscape and key players in the marketplace.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in the development of plans to align to seasonal buying decisions and product purchases.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take full ownership of the assigned product category, managing product selection, pricing, inventory, and overall performance to drive sales and profitability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with vendors to identify and select items and drive decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the rest of the buying team and other Fashion Nova team members to partner with new suppliers to bring the best products to our customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive exclusivity with vendors in products, terms, pricing, vendor-funded-markdowns, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and mentor assistant buyers in product selection, trend analysis, and vendor management while supporting their professional growth through skill development and career guidance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage ad hoc projects as assigned by management, ensuring timely execution and alignment with business objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
